Name: Rogue Fighter
About the game: Rogue Fighter is a fast paced room scale experience for the HTC Vive. Take control of a Fighter Plane gone rogue, fight your way through unending hordes of enemies. After clearing any resistance jump through a portal to a new section of space where greater threats await.
